3.	Write a program to create boxplot for all variables.

Solution:
> library(ggplot2)
> library(reshape)
> m1 <- melt(mtcars)
> ggplot(m1,aes(x = variable,y = value)) + facet_wrap(~variable) + geom_boxplot()
